  "body": "```\r\niPhone;\r\nApp version: 1.19.0 (20220328123004)\r\nApp comit: d6a6c41dd3ff06b057d2226644583ef57e7347da\r\nNode version: StatusIM/v0.97.3/ios-arm64/go1.16.9\r\n```\r\n\r\nWhen a DApp is connected to a custom chain the native coin balance (ETH balance) is not retrieved from that chain and shows as zero even if there is a balance.\r\nIn wallet page it also shows zero. Maybe it checks the balance from the main Ethereum chain.\r\nAnyway, due to that zero balance issue transactions can not be signed (no fee to pay).\r\n\r\nRelated with: https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/13281\r\n\r\n![WhatsApp Image 2022-05-26 at 4 06 11 PM](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8914034/170495518-f44f7f17-d584-4d04-8436-c8874c8359bd.jpeg)\r\n![WhatsApp Image 2022-05-26 at 4 06 15 PM](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8914034/170495533-5c938fdd-b7d8-435f-8c74-bd442c3ec98c.jpeg)\r\n\r\n",
